# Global defaults
Create Both
Expunge None
SyncState *

MaildirStore local-busybusiness
Path ~/.local/share/mail/personal/busybusiness/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/personal/busybusiness/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

MaildirStore local-services
Path ~/.local/share/mail/personal/services/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/personal/services/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

MaildirStore local-shopping
Path ~/.local/share/mail/personal/shopping/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/personal/shopping/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

MaildirStore local-max
Path ~/.local/share/mail/personal/max/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/personal/max/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

MaildirStore local-jointoit
Path ~/.local/share/mail/work/jointoit/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/work/jointoit/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore busybusiness
Host mail.netyaga.com
Port 993
User busybusiness@max.netyaga.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup service imap account busybusiness@max.netyaga.com host mail.netyaga.com"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore services
Host mail.netyaga.com
Port 993
User services@max.netyaga.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup service imap account services@max.netyaga.com host mail.netyaga.com"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore shopping
Host mail.netyaga.com
Port 993
User shopping@max.netyaga.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup service imap account shopping@max.netyaga.com host mail.netyaga.com"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore max
Host mail.netyaga.com
Port 993
User max@max.netyaga.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup service imap account max@max.netyaga.com host mail.netyaga.com"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore jointoit
Host mailing.jointoit.com
Port 143
User maksym.netiaha@jointoit.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup service imap account maksym.netiaha@jointoit.com host mailing.jointoit.com"
TLSType STARTTLS

Channel busybusiness
Far :busybusiness:
Near :local-busybusiness:
Patterns *

Channel services
Far :services:
Near :local-services:
Patterns *

Channel shopping
Far :shopping:
Near :local-shopping:
Patterns *

Channel max
Far :max:
Near :local-max:
Patterns *

Channel jointoit
Far :jointoit:
Near :local-jointoit:
Patterns *

Group personal
Channels busybusiness services shopping max

Group work
Channels jointoit
